title: Ep 19 - Believe in Yourself
itunes:title: Ep 19 - Believe in Yourself
description:
Believing in yourself is the first step on your road to success. You must believe in yourself before anyone else will. In this episode we speak about the importance of self talk as well as three steps to help you believe in yourself if you don't at the moment. We will also talk about something called "The Funeral For I Can't"
